{"tid":1079915,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"燒山：美國經濟非常健康，相反中國經濟有泡沫爆破危機","createTime":"2019-03-27T08:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T13:48:43.000Z","uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e0feddc59bd2d0209fe87e82ed39adb7b23931e6","tid":1079915,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T08:49:30.000Z","msg":"昨日蕭若元在其創辦的網台《謎米香港》發表18分鐘的影片，大談美債孳息率倒掛會否觸發衰退的問題。蕭若元斬釘截鐵地表示「今日嘅美國經濟，我要話畀大家聽，係非常健康嘅，點解？美國通貨膨脹率全部都係within forecast，你睇唔到點解會衰退。」更指，「其實只要冇一個泡沫爆破，今時今日美國經濟陷入衰退幾乎唔存在。」<br />\n<br />\n蕭若元解釋，自從格林斯潘年代開始，聯儲局懂得於經濟過熱之前超前控制通脹，而未於經濟衰退出現前便會提早減息，令經濟避免步入衰退。美國目前擁有非常多的數據，足夠作出即時反應。<br />\n<br />\n蕭若元認為，「真正嘅世界危機係中國泡沫爆破，中國而家估計負債七百幾萬億，係歷史上呢係未嘗試過有人咁多債，閉關咗害唔到出面，但佢自己嘅經濟需求contract，就會令到世界需求減少。」<br />\n<br />\n他不點名批評有人過去一年不停持續講，美國將會陷入大衰退、股市大跌，因為孳息曲綫將會倒掛。他認為，「講咗一年，如果你不停咁講，總有一日會靈&hellip;預言股市大跌，<span style=\"color: red;\">就好似沈大師預言樓市大跌，預言咗20年終有一日會跌。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190327/59418112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190327%2F59418112&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5d5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=8ee812ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190327%2F59418112&h=03209512\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190327/59418112</a>"},{"pid":"d9d1e8f506b5586c0d47d3fdee67c392ecfdee6a","tid":1079915,"uid":118623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T08:49:58.000Z","msg":"Molamola"},{"pid":"16e9c345218e57cabf2c51b3342bccb45d65116f","tid":1079915,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T08:50:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2_yUN5b-nMQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2_yUN5b-nMQ&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5d5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=c4cdd414\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2_yUN5b-nMQ</a>"},{"pid":"be95387385a005ed61550ab98bf674eca3b9180b","tid":1079915,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T08:50:50.000Z","msg":"Burn!!!!!!"},{"pid":"75a1dd756eebf3c8c4c7fd946275c117793d6e2b","tid":1079915,"uid":188155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cda37961fa9faeb73061c7fc190fe4fa49e252de","tid":1079915,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:37:15.000Z","msg":"燈美國 死仆街... 都岩的 老美係時侯跌下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e184ca435031e8fe454b8fe8fcef1b418ae90d61","tid":1079915,"uid":41423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:39:30.000Z","msg":"dllm燒山"},{"pid":"a6be18f9677cb8586b17565f56b293bd46ead3a5","tid":1079915,"uid":127807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"大撚膽！居然串師父！未死過！"},{"pid":"d70c298a540e41e1b312261ebc1ca6626b9d1627","tid":1079915,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"燈生，求下你出少句聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f53f43e8a34f2a50427d9ef7ec3de5c09b9809","tid":1079915,"uid":22337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T13:42:36.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b3204ce788253a4a271bf6dff4826c1623cdb5","tid":1079915,"uid":236038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T13:48:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}